Package com.amazonaws.kinesisvideo.common.logging

Class Log

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.amazonaws.kinesisvideo.common.logging.Log
  • public class Log
extends java.lang.Object
    Kinesis Video Streams common codebase. Logging class for Kinesis Video Streams codebase. The underlying logger can be different for different platforms - i.e. LogCat for Android.

    • Field Detail

      • SYSTEM_OUT

        public static final OutputChannel SYSTEM_OUT
        OutputChannel implementation based on System.out. This can be useful in JUnit tests, since they run in an environment that lacks a working implementation of actual logging mechanism.
